metadata.name: Lo-Fi Room #001
metadata.description:
A chill room made to evoke a feeling of calm and nostalgia. Everyone is welcome to relax in here.
These rooms are an advocate of perfections in the imperfections. 
Lo-Fi Rooms are made to send out a message that glitches are not be worried about, but accepted and embraced with positivity .

Come and Join us in this journey full of relaxation and love!
